Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是制作人小中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是「周刊少年JACK」编辑部的服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是服部哲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来代表原作者亚城木梦叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画「Reversi」还请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始介绍制作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 今天的工作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天动画就开播了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人感慨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亚城木君相处虽然只有三年的时间 但发生了好多事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 他们两个也没有参加什么后期录音的活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好像是说在顺利播放之前 什么都不打算参加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是亚城木君啊 该说是顽固呢 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 亚豆小姐也很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来很文静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 同类相投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩19个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就心跳不止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在试映会上不是看过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式播放时不也会心跳不止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城也心跳不止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 对最高来说在另一种意义上也心跳不止呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 另一种意义上？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天「Reversi」动画播完后就去见亚豆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保一句话都没跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让助手明天休息的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后明天就正式对亚豆求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 但回复100％是OK啊 也就不会紧张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么回事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不见面互相加油的两个人 他们梦想终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分量已经不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那时候求婚 不可能不紧张的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真城最高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种恍如隔世的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 今天的真城怎么了 该说是诚实还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很感谢香耶的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你握手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手？ 你想握已为人之妻的手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶酱 我很久就想和你说 现在是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶给我们起的“亚城木梦叶”这个笔名 一直激励着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚豆一定也是一样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没帮上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 香耶又帮忙打理家务 又帮我们工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么表扬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 是真城秋人还有美保才让我这么幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说谢的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之间也有话要说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 男人之间的对话什么的…没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后我们也像之前一样 延续「亚城木梦叶」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天「Reversi」动画开播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 一起看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说那个 播放完之后真城君会过来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 他要说「把美保交给我」么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样的话早就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也要和爸爸说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们是要约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许下了「实现梦想之后就结婚」的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直坚持不见面而努力到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么有趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你成为「JACK」上最有人气的作家的报告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在我又没有在周刊上连载
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的第一 不能说是真正的第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要给我拿来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…叔叔没能做到的事 想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要全部实现给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排拉面 我买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 好消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这周的速报说「GIRI」排第二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那不是不错么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第一名的「ZOMBI☆GUN」的差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是第二名的「GIRI」到\N第五位的「+NATURAL」几乎没什么差距
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只不过是陪衬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊 「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Reversi」完结之后一直都是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然「Reversi」就这么完结太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天动画就要开始了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说这么没出息的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要改变「JACK」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻师傅和亚城木君他们已经给了大家一个答复了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出大话的我不继续努力的话怎么像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周的速报 第8名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 心里负面要素好像不够啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起为什么 当然是因为太幸福了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个没志气的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超级漫画家的计划怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经减了10公斤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ 当然在考虑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也是到第二阶段的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ 第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么计划啊 连他本人我都完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我就边看亚城木老师的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边和优梨碳讨论幸福的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 之后再减掉40公斤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计 这次的小本也是第一名了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就连续13周第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 果然没有亚城木君就没办法燃起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我燃的很
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚城木老师回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚城木君的动画就要开始了 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看实现梦想的瞬间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了~！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~ 会赶不上的~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 请快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~ 如果赶不上都是妈妈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不久…再不久…和真城君的梦想就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中学3年级时候开始的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无选择了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然目的相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想法完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(518,440)}Weisse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么后会有期 白恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(446,440)}Schwartz
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黑恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类灭亡的游戏 就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片头曲好帅呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年后赶超新妻英治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念你曾经说过的这样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心给其他编辑压力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得川口先生也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改变世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事情 谁都不可能做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连世界的规则都难以遵守的人又怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}昨天的数学题 有些地方我还是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现了 和真城君的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减分制度？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 学生有20点基础分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果违反校规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据内容相应的减分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分数无法回复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 分数低于0分的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将被勒令退学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守规则是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连后藤老师你也…你知道你在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的话就干脆放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 你是学生会长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界也不是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的话是实话 我就真不能放任不管了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(456,440)}Weisse
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 白恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你签订契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约事项\N条例1\N与恶魔定下契约的人，可以将自己的想法传染给他人。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想真的实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 就只剩下求婚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么有点紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了~！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是美保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在亚豆的家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我明白了 这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 为什么这么慌张？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是以往的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 你非常漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豪华的车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不像真城君的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当上一流的漫画家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就向春野求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 反正要做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就开高级进口车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边最好的座位要留给春野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候 我坐在春野邻桌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我人生中最幸福的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面了 虽然心跳很快 但是感觉挺安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我坐在你身边的时候 也非常舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 中学的时候 和你同桌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最幸福的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…非常的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你坐一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在电车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都坐在我右边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在向春野求婚的时候再营造出那种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在外国汽车里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是川口太郎叔叔的愿望之一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他在日记上写到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见喜欢的人的时候要开高级的外国汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他却一直无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想实现他的愿望 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶座在左边实在太好了 可以让亚豆坐在右边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「实在太好了」 真像是真城君的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚豆小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开车了 请系好安全带…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真城君的叔叔过来见那个人的话 肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们两人仅仅只是到交换信件就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到充满两人回忆的地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚的话就可以很自然地说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合两人敞开心扉 最真实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 还是亚豆的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为是妈妈喜欢的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说早晚会回来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君 为什么要来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第一次和亚豆说话的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来绘画 他来负责原作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的肯定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次说话也是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在毕业式那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满两人回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不就和毕业式那天同样的情况了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能站在那里什么话也说不出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经24岁了 再也不是中学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 给我说出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结…结婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚还太早呢 毕竟才24岁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在说什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…我不能自然地说出这话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地说话到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好10年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一次在这里说话开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不说出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真城君完全没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像10年前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了大人 梦想也实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管自己身边的事物不断地变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真城君完全没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有变化实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最适合两人敞开心扉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚豆小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的漫画动画化后 其主角声优由亚豆来担当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这个梦想实现后 我们就结婚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个约定 你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 我们就一直在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恭喜你 平丸先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}苍树小姐 恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很适合你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}平丸先生 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}吉田先生你哭得太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}羡慕死你啦 平丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}平丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}以后要幸福地在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一也碳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好的 优梨碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所以说要创作比「+NATURAL」更好的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}总是沿用以前的东西才会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所以要准备一两个点子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}3个 4个 已经准备好5个点子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高滨君！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}来啦 来啦 终于来了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「正义的伙伴」电影化的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}虽然细节还在讨论中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但听说高层有这个意向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那我就把这个提交到连载会议上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 不要输给服部前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「PCP」最近越来越有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谢谢你的赞扬！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你习惯新婚的生活了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊…还没呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}嘛…那个屋子这么大 两个人平静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}还是说小两口还保持着距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哈哈 实现了梦想真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一辈子靠漫画吃饭才是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在此之前只是赌徒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}川口太郎是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那么 为了这个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我要开始鉴赏你们的新作了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}麻烦你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}决定连载后 就是结婚式了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}还得等定下之后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}叔叔他没说要我成为漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我是凭着自己意愿去画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}梦想 并不是别人说给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己想要实现的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画「爆漫王」这就是剧终了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那么最高和亚豆的结婚式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那哪能让别人看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家一直以后对我们的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会一直追求自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拭目以待！
